Package org.wmn4j.notation

Interface Part

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Measure>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiStaffPart, SingleStaffPart
    public interface Part
extends java.lang.Iterable<Measure>
    Represents a part in a score.

    Implementations of this class are expected to be thread-safe.

      • getMeasureCount

        int getMeasureCount()
        Returns the number of measures in this part. The count is based on the measure numbers, so even if a part has multiple staves its measure count is the largest measure number.
        Returns:
        number of measures in the part. If there is a pickup measure, it is included in the count.

      • getFullMeasureCount

        int getFullMeasureCount()
        Returns the the number of complete measures. Does not include the measure number if there is one.
        Returns:
        the number of measures excluding the pickup measure
